            "title": "Intro",
            "id": 71395,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>HTML também nos permite adicionar imagens a uma página da web.</p><webview version=\"2\" visible-if=\"always\" content=\"&lt;!doctype html&gt;&#xA;&lt;html&gt;&#xA; &lt;head&gt;&#xA;  &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;style.css&quot;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;style&gt;&#xA;   body {&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   img {&#xA;    border: solid gray 10px;&#xA;    margin: 10px;&#xA;    padding: 5px;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   h2 {&#xA;    width: 250px;&#xA;    margin: auto;&#xA;   }&#xA;  &lt;/style&gt;&#xA; &lt;/head&gt;&#xA; &lt;body&gt;&#xA;  &lt;h2&gt;Photography competition winner&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img&#xA;   style=&quot;width: 200px;&quot; src=&quot;https://mimo.app/i/fox.png&quot;&gt;&#xA; &lt;/body&gt;&#xA;&lt;/html&gt;\" /></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Images",
            "id": 58841,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para adicionar <strong>imagens</strong> a uma página da web, começamos com a tag <code>&lt;img&gt;</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"h3\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Drawing of \" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"em\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Earthrise\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"em\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"h3\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"img\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"40\" endIndex=\"45\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&lt;a&gt;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>&lt;img&gt;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Images",
            "id": 58835,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Assim como <code>&lt;br&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;img&gt;</code> é uma <strong>tag vazia</strong>. Isso significa que não tem uma tag de fechamento.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"h3\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Drawing of \" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"em\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Earthrise\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"em\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"h3\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"img\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"40\" endIndex=\"41\" /><option startIndex=\"41\" endIndex=\"44\" /><option startIndex=\"44\" endIndex=\"45\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&lt;img&gt;&lt;/img&gt;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>&lt;</code> seguido de <code>img</code> e finalmente <code>&gt;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Images",
            "id": 58836,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para exibir uma imagem, uma tag de imagem precisa do atributo <code>src</code>. <code>src</code> significa fonte.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"h3\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Drawing of \" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"em\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Earthrise\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"em\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"h3\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"img\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"src\" class=\"attr\" /><text value=\"=\" /><text value=\"&quot;https://mimo.app/i/earth.png&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"45\" endIndex=\"48\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"source\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>src</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Source",
            "id": 58911,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Nós definimos a imagem que queremos exibir com um sinal de <code>=</code> e o endereço da imagem entre aspas duplas.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"h3\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Drawing of \" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"em\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Earthrise\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"em\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"h3\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"img\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"src\" class=\"attr\" /><text value=\"=\" /><text value=\"&quot;https://mimo.app/i/earth.png&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"45\" endIndex=\"48\" /><option startIndex=\"48\" endIndex=\"49\" /><option startIndex=\"49\" endIndex=\"79\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"source\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>src</code> seguido de <code>=</code> e finalmente <code>\"https://mimo.app/i/earth.png\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Width",
            "id": 58839,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Podemos usar atributos para alterar o tamanho das imagens. Os atributos <code>width</code> e <code>height</code> usam pixels como a unidade de medida padrão.</p><p> Por exemplo, para definir a largura desta imagem como 100px, codifique <code>width = \"100\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"img\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"src\" class=\"attr\" /><text value=\"=\" /><text value=\"&quot;https://mimo.app/i/earth.png&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"width\" class=\"attr\" /><text value=\"=\" /><text value=\"&quot;100&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"height\" class=\"attr\" /><text value=\"=\" /><text value=\"&quot;200&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"40\" endIndex=\"45\" /><option startIndex=\"45\" endIndex=\"46\" /><option startIndex=\"46\" endIndex=\"51\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&lt;100&gt;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>width</code> seguido de <code>=</code> e finalmente <code>\"100\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Height",
            "id": 58840,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>E o atributo <code>height</code> ajusta a <strong>altura</strong> de uma imagem.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"img\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"src\" class=\"attr\" /><text value=\"=\" /><text value=\"&quot;https://mimo.app/i/earth.png&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"width\" class=\"attr\" /><text value=\"=\" /><text value=\"&quot;200&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"height\" class=\"attr\" /><text value=\"=\" /><text value=\"&quot;300&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" &gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"52\" endIndex=\"58\" /></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>height</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
