            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Escolha a tag correta para uma imagem.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"img\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"src\" class=\"attr\" /><text value=\"=\" /><text value=\"&quot;https://mimo.app/i/cafe.png&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"1\" /><option startIndex=\"1\" endIndex=\"4\" /><option startIndex=\"5\" endIndex=\"8\" /><option startIndex=\"8\" endIndex=\"9\" /><option startIndex=\"9\" endIndex=\"38\" /><option startIndex=\"38\" endIndex=\"39\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&lt;/img&gt;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>&lt;</code> seguido de <code>img</code> e depois <code>src</code>, <code>=</code>, <code>\"https://mimo.app/i/cafe.png\"</code>, <code>&gt;</code>.</p></body></html>"
